      </card>
      <card>
        <question><p>Is a negative index valid for an <code>ArrayList</code>?</p></question>
        <answer><p>No. A negative index causes an <code>IndexOutOfBoundsException</code>.</p></answer>
        <distractor><p>Yes — negative indexes count from the end of the list.</p></distractor>
        <distractor><p>Yes, but only <code>-1</code> is allowed; it returns the last element.</p></distractor>
