      </card>
    </cards>

    <cards>
      <ek>Changing the size of an `ArrayList` while traversing it using an enhanced `for` loop will cause a `ConcurrentModificationException` to be thrown. When using an enhanced `for` loop to traverse an `ArrayList`, you should not add or remove elements.</ek>

      <card>
